
Fork - https://sourceforge.net/p/dar/mailman/message/1043472/ (https://mail.gnome.org/archives/mc-devel/2006-April/msg00001.html)


== INSTALL ==

1. Put udar from extfs.d to $(libexecdir)/mc/extfs.d/ or in ~/.mc/extfs.d/

Ubuntu:
* /usr/lib/mc/extfs.d

2. Add content mc.ext.

mc.ext >> /etc/mc/mc.ext or mc.ext >> ~/.mc.ext

